name: Dollar Bill Holder.
description:
This piece is #4 of 5 pieces from "Black & White Nights: The Afterparty"; a limited edition, cross-platform, companion collection to "Black & White Nights".

Taken at a nightclub in SOHO in 2013. A burlesque dancer shows off her tattoo and night's tips.

The other 4 pieces from "Black & White Nights: The Afterparty" will be available via auctions on Opensea, Rarible, Kalamint and Foundation.

Owning one of these 5 limited edition pieces gets you a VIP private sale slot for my upcoming drop "Black & White Days".

The 5 owners of "Black & White Nights: The Afterparty" will be the first five people to select any piece they like from "Black & White Days" before I release it to the public, and I'll give them that piece for free.

Yes...FREE.
